<h2>Welcome to The Countdown Tracker</h2>
<p>The Countdown Tracker is a web app that allows an MC in <a href="http://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/171286/The-Sprawl----MIDNIGHT">The Sprawl</a> to Create, Delete, Advance, 
and Reset Countdown Clocks, and share the results with his players.


<h3>How it works:</h3>

<p>The MC clicks the green <b>Create</b> button below to create a new Countdown Controller and Big Board. 

<p>They then share the link to The Big Board with their players (via Email, TXT, SMS, etc), and use the
Countdown Controller screen to manage their game's Countdown Clocks.  Modifications made to the clocks 
are instantly transmitted to the Big Board through the magic of <a href="http://lmgtfy.com/?q=websockets">WebSockets</a>.  

<h3>Important Note for MC's:</h3>

<p>When you create a Countdown Contoller it is identified by a unique URL.  You are the <i>only</i> 
person in the universe that knows it.  If you lose it, it's gone forever.  There is no way to get it 
back. So Bookmark it, email it to yourself, write it on a PostIt and stick it on your monitor.  
Do whatever it takes to keep track of it.  
<p> Also, the Countdown Controller page isn't really designed to be shared (it only transmits changes 
to the Big Board, it doesn't listen for them). If you need to share the Countdowns, share the Big 
Board Link.    

